Helen C. GAMBLE, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. DAISY PRODUCTS, Inc., and Joseph N. Lowe and Mollie L. Grossman, Defendants-Appellees. No. 42. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 21, 1932. Henry J. Lueke, of New York City (Frank Toohey, of counsel), for appellant. George L. Wheeloek, of New York City (Thomas Ewing, of New York City, of counsel), for appellees.

Before MANTON, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decision affirmed.
